desc
@request function is main function of block driver
it continuosly check the request in queue
if any request is present the it called transfer function which handle actual data io
the parameter for transfer function is pointer to current request
starting position of sector from where data write started
third argument states about upto which position data to be write
fourth argument states about data is read/write from block device it simply indicates direction
@


